@startuml PolyMind - Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Vue.js" as Vue
participant "Symfony" as Symfony
participant "FastAPI Router" as FastAPI
participant "AI APIs\n(OpenAI/Claude/Gemini)" as AI

User -> Vue : Send prompt
Vue -> Symfony : POST /api/chat
Symfony -> Symfony : Auth + validate JWT
Symfony -> FastAPI : POST /route\n{prompt, user_id}
FastAPI -> AI : Analyze intent\n(routing LLM call)
FastAPI -> AI : Route to best model
AI --> FastAPI : AI response
FastAPI --> Symfony : Return response + model used
Symfony --> Vue : Save history + respond
Vue --> User : Display response + show model used

@enduml
